Class FloatStaticHistogram

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.datastructures.histogram.AbstractStaticHistogram

    FloatHistogram, Histogram
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FloatDynamicHistogram

    public class FloatStaticHistogram
extends AbstractStaticHistogram
implements FloatHistogram
    Histogram class storing float values. The histogram will start with "bin" bins, but it can grow dynamically to the left and right.
    Since:
    0.5.5
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
